  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to assess the efficacy of DEPREXIL administration in combination
      with relaxation psychotherapy in the treatment of patients with signs and symptoms of
      depression. The duration of this double-blind placebo controlled phase 3 clinical trial will
      be 24 weeks. The estimated number of persons to be recruited and randomized for the study is
      200.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
